objects.description:
Define apple in the real world.

Apple is an open source operating system designed to be used on the Mac. However, it is also being used by Apple Computer’s iPhone and iPad. Apple used the technology from Microsoft to launch the iPhone. Therefore, Apple is using the technology from Microsoft and they are trying to license it with Microsoft.

The question: does Apple have to license Windows to the iPhone and iPad? The answer is yes. And it also covers every version.
